  <name translate="no">MQTTy</name>
  <summary>Connect to an MQTT broker and Pub/Sub to topics</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A native GUI MQTT Client, useful for debugging MQTT topics, as well as a system notification
      producer/consumer. With support for sending plaintext/JSON messages and syntax highlighting
      support.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pub/Sub to topics seamlessly</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
